message.body: Three things: (1) Hi! (2) I woke up this morning thinking it was Sunday--awful feeling. (3) I did wake up smiling first because I'm going to marry you :D
Hi! Hope you feel better, darling! And sorry its Monday :-/ But same thing happened to me! Twas a crap day of work, but i thought of you nd got rull happy haha
Yes it 'twas! But I can't wait to see you on Saturday!!! Just gotta get through Wednesday and I'm good. Just get through Wednesday.
Haha we're both saying that :) Bring on Saturday plz plz plz. Hope youre ready for the day, my love. See you so so soon. Hug, kiss, and head scratch. Yours.
I completely agree!!! Especially with the head scratching thing :D
Haha oh hrs and hrs and hrs
I'm going to hold you to that!
Good morning, Jenny. I love you with all my heart. One night closer.
